#   - Get card image: GET /api/card-images/{cardId}/image
#   - Mark printed: POST /api/printing/mark-printed/{userId}
#   - Mark collected: POST /api/printing/mark-collected/{userId}
#   - Verify fingerprint: POST /api/verify/fingerprint
#
# LOCAL DEV: Capture app runs on localhost:5001
#   - CAPTURE_APP_OUTPUT_DIR: Only used by capture app for local file output (not used in production)
#

